                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9706" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1459</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">796 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“取山地之材，做中国面包”—石头先生的烤炉品牌崛起之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Taking Mountain Materials to Make Chinese Bread&quot; - The Rise of the Mr. Stone&#39;s Oven Brand</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马春爱，吴成岩，孙凤全，肖天祎，王瀚超，张庆丽，肖尧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东石头先生的烤炉餐饮管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌定位；目标市场细分；品牌价值塑造；品牌价值传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Brand Positioning; Target Market Segmentation; Brand Value Shaping; Brand Value Communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石头先生的烤炉于2014年在山东创立，旨在提供“好吃，放心”的烘焙产品，凭借手工制作与高品质原料赢得消费者认可，在山东取得成功后，进军京沪等地，不断发展壮大。石头先生的烤炉采取了多种做法来进行品牌价值塑造。定位上，确立“中高端的本土化欧式面包”方向，融合本土食材，打破口感隔阂；针对不同客群，构建差异化渠道布局，精准匹配需求；坚持中央工厂日配模式，建立自有物流和培训中心来确保品质；同时注重产品和管理流程创新，积极与顾客进行情感互动，多措并举来塑造品牌形象。本案例通过石头先生的烤炉品牌崛起历程，帮助学生理解跨文化产品如何确定自身定位，引导学生思考品牌在发展过程中如何进行品牌价值塑造和传播，掌握品牌管理理论与方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Mr. Stone&#39;s Oven was founded in Shandong in 2014, aiming to provide &quot;delicious and reassuring&quot; baked products. It won the consumer recognition with handcrafting and high-quality raw materials. After succeeding in Shandong, it expanded into Beijing, Shanghai, and other regions, continuously growing. Mr. Stone&#39;s Oven adopted diverse approaches for brand-value shaping. In positioning, it established the direction of localized mid-to-high-end European bread, integrating local ingredients to break taste barriers. For different customer groups, it constructs a differentiated channel layout to precisely match demands. It adhered to the central-factory daily-distribution model, establishing its own logistics and training centers to ensure quality. Meanwhile, it emphasizes product and management-process innovation, actively interacting emotionally with customers to shape the brand image. This case, through the rise process of Mr. Stone&#39;s Oven brand, helps students understand how cross-cultural products determine their own positioning, guides students to think about how to carry out brand value shaping and communication during the brand development process, and masters brand management theories and methods.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨文化适应理论；STP理论；4P营销理论；CBBE模型；整合营销传播理论；消费者学习理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
